    • openFileOnDemand

      public boolean openFileOnDemand​(java.lang.String filename)
      User has asked that a file be opened. find the LoadAndSaveFileType plugin that can do it, and then try. The loader might spawn a new thread and return before the load is actually finished.
      Parameters:
      filename - the file to be opened.
      Returns:
      true if file was loaded successfully. false if it failed.
